item.title: I need major help D:
item.dc:creator: @m1lkman m1lkman
item.description:
@m1lkman wrote:

For Client:
Copy: Class8.java, and all of the models in the “models” folder.
Paste: Into your basic deltascape files, put models inyour modes folder.
For server:
Copy: Item.cfg and itemHandler.java in your pro source files.
Paste: Item.cfg into your configs folder and itemhandler.java where the run.bat is.

This, if you’re lucky, will cmpile with no errors. I suggest making a backup.
